      "content": "the grants and stuff sound good on paper but most of these guys say they're too slow or too hard to actually get. if you look at it from the perspective of a local business owner who is just trying to keep the lights on next month, doesn't it seem like these regulations prioritize abstract environmental goals over the actual survival of the local economy?",
